code: /**  * Sets the license  *  * @param license license  * @return this builder  */ public PutLicenseRequestBuilder setLicense(License license) {     request.license(license).     return this. }
public PutLicenseRequestBuilder setLicense(BytesReference licenseSource, XContentType xContentType) {     request.license(licenseSource, xContentType).     return this. }
